  <summary>9/27/2006--Passed House amended.
HOPE VI Reauthorization Act of 2006 - Amends the United States Housing Act of 1937 to extend through FY2007 grants for demolition, site revitalization, replacement housing, and tenant-based assistance for severely distressed public housing projects. Extends the sunset date for such assistance to September 30, 2007.</summary>
